title: AOC I2779VH Monitor Review Part 2
description:

AOC Monitor Unboxing: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=f8lSBZbR678 

Desktop Review: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=A_2MonTN0zg 

View brilliant media content with this 27-inch AOC LED monitor. Its Full HD resolution and mega dynamic contrast ratio of 20,000,000:1 provides crisp image details, and it connects to high-definition A/V equipment with its VGA and HDMI inputs. This AOC LED monitor has a Kensington security slot to help prevent theft.
